extends dashboardlayout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #{title}
 
  
  p This will have a CRUD facility for the group to indicate what tasks need to be tended to around the garden.

  p By default it will request to view all of the posts from the task list database and will display them here.
  
  p There will also be links to page to Create (task_create.pug), Edit (task_edit.pug) and Delete (task_delete.pug) entries to the Task list
   
  a(href='/task_create') Create Task list item
  br
  a(href='/task_edit') Edit Task list item
  br
  a(href='/task_delete') Delete Task list item
  br
  a(href='/task') View Task list items